Enumeration Type Documentation

enum rpmRC_e

Package read return codes.

Enumerator:
RPMRC_OK 

Generic success code

RPMRC_NOTFOUND 

Generic not found code.

RPMRC_FAIL 

Generic failure code.

RPMRC_NOTTRUSTED 

Signature is OK, but key is not trusted.

RPMRC_NOKEY 

Public key is unavailable.
